        <li><strong>Liu He (六合) — Secret Friend:</strong> The {{ yearData.animal }}'s "secret friend" is the <a href="/zodiac/{{ yearData.liuHe }}/">{{ yearData.liuHe | capitalize }}</a>, a pairing that creates deep, intuitive understanding.</li>
        <li><strong>Six Clash (六衝):</strong> The <a href="/zodiac/{{ yearData.clash }}/">{{ yearData.clash | capitalize }}</a> sits directly opposite the {{ yearData.animal }} on the zodiac wheel. This creates tension but also complementary growth potential.</li>
